  "An electrical circuit has impedance Z = -3 + 4i ohms. An engineer needs the impedance in polar form for analysis. What is the modulus?": "电路有阻力 Z = - 3 + 4 i ohms。 工程师需要极性阻力来进行分析。 什么是模量?",
