  "A telecommunications engineer represents a signal as z = 6 cis 240°. She needs to express z² in rectangular form for further processing. What is z²?": "电信工程师表示一个信号为z = 6cis 240°。她需要以矩形形式表示z2,以便进一步处理。Z2是什么?",
